data.title: Annual Awards
data.text:
USA Hockey's Annual Meeting is the yearly gathering of USA Hockey’s volunteer leaders, including members of the organization’s board of directors, councils, committees and sections.

USA Hockey will announce its list of annual award winners on Wednesday, May 29. The winners will be recognized during the President's Award Dinner on Friday, June 7, at the Denver Marriott Tech Center as part of USA Hockey's Annual Meeting..
